content: Use to love this app but after starting shibboleth again and renewing my membership I can no longer open it! At all. I get the starting picture and then I get a message that say the journal keeps stopping. I've reinstalled several times with no luck.
This app really helps track your progress and is easy to use!
Horrible there is no way to set up an account if you dont already have one.
It just keep saying synchronizing records. Please, help!
I really want to use this app but it keeps stating synchronizing records and never allows me to access the food lists or recipes Please help
I love this app. I can find approved foods when I go to the grocery store and find how to approve foods at restaurants in my area. I can log what I eat easily to keep me accountable.

user unfriendly. will not show anything other "synchronizing your records" im already over it and ive had it for 2 days trying to figure it out. this is one thing i will be deleting and not depending on.

This app is awesome...i could not live without it..once you learn the 
program. it helps with staying on track journaling and grocery shopping
Im glad I'm back on program

Absolutely love the app and love the Shibboleth plan. I have lost 40 pounds 
and journaling is a big reason why. The app makes it easy to journal and 
look up necessary information. Would love to have access to the weekly 
timing chart and the weight graph in the app but it is awesome without

This app is a HUGE help in entering items into my online journal.  Makes searching for approved recipes and foods a breeze. It is a great tool while shopping.
